OL,7,FOn 19 October, just like on the day he
OL,8,Fdied, he had soiled himself. That day,
OL,9,Fthough, Robinson, 30, did not shake
OL,10,Fhim, or beat him with a cane. She
OL,11,Fdeliberately and forcibly lowered him
OL,12,Finto a bath of scalding-hot water.
OL,14,FThe ordeal, a "textbook" example of
OL,15,Fforced immersion in hot water, left
OL,16,FDwelaniyah with burns on his legs and
OL,17,Fbottom covering between 15% and 20% of
OL,18,Fhis body. Much of this burning was the
OL,19,Fhighest-category "full thickness" burn
OL,20,Fthat would have been "extremely
OL,21,Fdebilitating, extremely painful".
