OL,7,FBut Robinson did not take her son to
OL,8,Fhospital. Instead she treated his
OL,9,Fburns at their home in Ushaw Moor,
OL,10,FCounty Durham, using aloe vera gel and
OL,11,Fbandages, relying on internet searches
OL,12,Ffor "natural remedies to burn wounds"
OL,13,Fand "how to treat first degree minor
OL,14,Fburns".
OL,16,FOver the following days she bought
OL,17,Fbandages, dressings, Nurofen and
OL,18,Fhydrocolloid dressings from Amazon.
