OL,10,Fsaid. "There was no crying, no
OL,11,Fshouting."
OL,13,FWhile Dwelaniyah was suffering, his
OL,14,Ffather, Gabriel Adu-Appau, 33, was
OL,15,Foblivious to the cruelty being
