OL,10,Fwith her lover, Innocent Onoja, 27,
OL,11,Ffrom Middlesbrough, who she had met on
OL,12,Fthe dating app OkCupid.
OL,14,FA week and a half after burning him,
OL,15,Fon 28 October, with his injuries still
OL,16,Funtreated, she told Mr Onoja that
OL,17,FDwelaniyah needed "an ass kicking".
OL,18,FShe complained that he had soiled
OL,19,Fhimself, and that he had spilled her
OL,20,Fmedication on the floor.
