OL,7,FDespite her little boy being
OL,8,Funconscious, Christina Robinson did
OL,9,Fnot call an ambulance immediately.
OL,10,FInstead she sent a WhatsApp message to
OL,11,FDwelaniyah's father, Gabriel Adu-
OL,12,FAppau, saying "call me please". Then,
OL,13,Fafter trying to call him, she searched
OL,14,FYouTube for videos on "how to
OL,15,Fresuscitate a child".
OL,17,FFifteen minutes after that first
OL,18,Fmessage, Mr Adu-Appau phoned her back
OL,19,Fand, after a three-minute
OL,20,Fconversation, he told her to phone an
OL,21,Fambulance.
